---
import SectionHeading from "./SectionHeading.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import headshot from "../assets/images/headshot.jpeg";
---

<section id="about" class="py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
    <SectionHeading title="About" />
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-center">
      <Image
        src={headshot}
        alt="Sean Higgins"
        width={160}
        height={160}
        class="h-40 w-40 shrink-0 rounded-2xl object-cover"
      />
      <div class="space-y-4 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
        <p>
          Software engineer with a M.S. in Software Engineering and a B.S. in
          Computer Science from Loyola University Chicago. Currently working on
          a high-performing enterprise platform team building authentication and
          API gateway infrastructure at scale. I enjoy building clean, practical
          software and have experience across front-end, back-end, data
          engineering, and machine learning.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not writing code, you can find me in the boxing ring, on the
          mountain snowboarding, enjoying a live concert, or at home building furniture and making
          art. World traveler. Eagle Scout. Cat dad to Sunny.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
